    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>EARNED-INCOME CREDIT</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Angela Starita</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Starita, Angela</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>New Jersey Gov Christine Whitman signs legislation giving low-income families earned-income tax credit, effective immediately (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Governor Whitman signed legislation last week giving low-income families an earned-income tax credit, adding to the federal tax credit they already receive. Effective immediately, the credit will benefit almost  240,000 families with children and an annual income of $20,000 or less a year.  When the tax credit is fully implemented by 2003, each family will receive a credit equal to 20 percent of its federal tax credit, up to $800.</p>
        <p>Angela Starita</p>
      </block>
